# PCB Bill of Materials — Self-Balancing Articulated Leg Robot
**Distribution & Interface Board — 4-Layer, Compact**
**Designer:** DOUDOU | **Date:** 2026-05-26 | **Revision:** A

---

## 1. Project Overview

This PCB is a **signal/power/filtering/connector distribution board**. It does not contain any full H-bridge, motor driver IC, or high-current switching circuitry on-board. All high-power loads connect via screw terminals to external modules.

### System Topology
```
3S Li-ion Battery (11.1V nom, 12.6V max, ~9.0V cutoff)
        │
        ├─ [F1: 15A Fuse] ─ [Q1: AO4407A Reverse Polarity MOSFET]
        │                              │
        │           ┌──────────────────┼──────────────────┐
        │           │                  │                  │
        │      [XL4016-A]         [XL4016-B]         [J2/J3]
        │      6V / 10A           5V / 10A           VBAT direct
        │      4× MG996R          RPi 5 + Logic      L298N H-bridge
        │      Servos             ESP32               DC Motors
        │
        └── [AMS1117-3.3]  ← fed from 5V rail
               3.3V / 1A
               ESP32 VCC, MPU-6500, logic ICs
```

