### 3.1 Protection & Power Input

| Ref | Qty | Component | Value/Part | Package | Description |
|-----|-----|-----------|------------|---------|-------------|
| J1 | 1 | Screw Terminal | 2-pin, 5.08mm | KF301-2P | VBAT battery input |
