| Q1 | 1 | P-Channel MOSFET | AO4407A | SO-8 | Reverse polarity protection |
| R5 | 1 | Resistor | 10kΩ 1% | 0603 | Gate voltage divider — upper (Source to Gate) |
| R6 | 1 | Resistor | 10kΩ 1% | 0603 | Gate voltage divider — lower (Gate to GND) |
| D1 | 1 | TVS Diode | SMAJ5.0A or equiv | SMA (DO-214AC) | 3.3V rail transient protection |

**AO4407A Gate Divider Design:**
```
Source (VBAT, up to 12.6V) ──[R5: 10kΩ]──► Gate
                                               │
                                          [R6: 10kΩ]
                                               │
                                              GND
Vgs = -(VBAT × R6/(R5+R6)) = -(VBAT/2)
At 12.6V full charge: Vgs = -6.3V ✅ (AO4407A rated ±20V)
At 11.1V nominal:     Vgs = -5.55V ✅ (well within saturation)
```

