### 3.4 MPU-6500 IMU (GY-6500 Module — SPI Mode)

| Ref | Qty | Component | Value/Part | Package | Description |
|-----|-----|-----------|------------|---------|-------------|
| J5 | 1 | Female Pin Header | 1×8 pins, 2.54mm | Through-hole | GY-6500 module socket |
| R7 | 1 | Resistor | 33Ω | 0603 | SPI_CLK series damping resistor |
| R8 | 1 | Resistor | 33Ω | 0603 | SPI_MOSI series damping resistor |
| R9 | 1 | Resistor | 33Ω | 0603 | SPI_MISO series damping resistor |
| R10 | 1 | Resistor | 33Ω | 0603 | SPI_CS series damping resistor |
| C5 | 1 | Capacitor | 100nF ceramic | 0603 | IMU VCC HF decoupling |
| C6 | 1 | Capacitor | 10µF electrolytic | 0805 | IMU VCC bulk cap |

**GY-6500 J5 Pin Header (8 pins):**

| Pin | Net | Notes |
|-----|-----|-------|
| 1 | +3V3 | Module VCC |
| 2 | GND | Module GND |
| 3 | SPI_SCL | SCLK from ESP32 GPIO18 (via R7) |
| 4 | SPI_SDA | MOSI from ESP32 GPIO23 (via R8) |
| 5 | SPI_SDO | MISO to ESP32 GPIO19 (via R9) |
| 6 | SPI_CS | CS from ESP32 GPIO5 (via R10) |
| 7 | IMU_INT | Interrupt to ESP32 GPIO4 |
| 8 | GND | FSYNC → GND (disable frame sync) |

**SPI Mode Enable:** NCS pin (module pin 6) = LOW → enables SPI mode automatically.
NCS HIGH = I2C mode. NCS LOW = SPI mode + chip select.

